How to Read This Manual
***********************

   This document contains two parts. The first part explains the design
and the history of the `stools' package. The second part provides step
by step instructions how the `stools' package can be extended.

   This memo does not provide a detailed description of the various
tools and their command line options. The reader is referred to the
manual pages for these details.


