Problems
********

   If you find a bug in `stools', please send electronic mail to
`stools@ibr.cs.tu-bs.de'.  Include the version number, which you can
find by running `stools --version'.  Also include in your message the
output that the program produced and the output you expected.

   If you have other questions, comments or suggestions about `stools',
contact the author via electronic mail to `schoenw@ibr.cs.tu-bs.de'.
The author will try to help you out, although he may not have time to
fix your problems.


